      public int updata(int level, double rate)
      Updata the level i with the new rate.
      参数:
      level - The level need to updata.
      rate - The new rate.
      返回:
      0 for updata succeed, 1 for the rate is not in [0, 1] and 2 for level is not in the tax table.
